Output demo.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20

# Enter fix mode
Type "fix"
Enter
Sleep 3s

# Demo 1: Auto-correct a typo
Type "owd"
Enter
Sleep 4s

# Demo 2: Natural language
Type "? show me nested tree from here"
Enter
Sleep 6s

# Demo 3: Long mode
Type "?? how many lines of py code in this project?"
Enter
Sleep 10s

# Exit
Type "exit"
Enter
Sleep 1s
